# Identity (NEVER commit) — age private key that decrypts secrets.age.
.age-key

# Encrypted vault — user policy: keep OUT of git, transfer manually.
# Even though secrets.age is ciphertext (safe with .age-key absent),
# user preference is no secrets in repo at all. Transfer both files
# between machines via password manager / encrypted USB / scp.
secrets.age

